# ICPro — Schema Markup / SEO

## Objective
Add structured data (Schema.org) to blog posts to enable rich results in Google Search.

## Status: PARTIALLY COMPLETE

## Validator Status
- Google Rich Results Test: https://search.google.com/test/rich-results — FAILING ❌
- Schema.org Validator: https://validator.schema.org/ — PASSING ✅

## Schema Template (BlogPosting)

```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@graph": [
    {
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "@id": "https://cerkl.com/blog/<<slug>>",
      "mainEntityOfPage": {
        "@type": "WebPage",
        "@id": "https://cerkl.com/blog/<<slug>>"
      },
      "headline": "<<meta-title>>",
      "description": "<<seo-meta-description>>",
      "image": "<<header-image>>",
      "author": {
        "@id": "https://cerkl.com/#organization"
      },
      "publisher": {
        "@id": "https://cerkl.com/#organization"
      },
      "datePublished": "<<published-on>>",
      "dateModified": "<<updated-on>>",
      "keywords": "<<primary-keyword>>",
      "articleSection": "<<categories:name>>"
    },
    {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "@id": "https://cerkl.com/#organization",
      "name": "Cerkl",
      "url": "https://cerkl.com",
      "logo": {
        "@type": "ImageObject",
        "url": "https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/691f7a33d90467d9ab273404/69a3822cd8cb1f93e36c4bd9_cerkl_wordmark.png"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

